{"PageNumber":17,"Angle":0,"RotatedAngle":0,"Height":1620,"Width":2880,"OriginHeight":0,"OriginWidth":0,"Elements":[{"Index":0,"Type":"title","Text":"#  Access control matrices: cons","Level":0,"Polygon":{"LeftBottom":{"X":211,"Y":308},"LeftTop":{"X":211,"Y":185},"RightBottom":{"X":1783,"Y":308},"RightTop":{"X":1783,"Y":185}},"InsetImageName":"","Elements":null,"ImagePath":"","group_id":-1,"group_type":""},{"Index":1,"Type":"paragraph","Text":"● There is a fairly big disadvantage to the access control matrix: it can get really big","Level":0,"Polygon":{"LeftBottom":{"X":222,"Y":576},"LeftTop":{"X":222,"Y":427},"RightBottom":{"X":2515,"Y":576},"RightTop":{"X":2515,"Y":427}},"InsetImageName":"","Elements":null,"ImagePath":"","group_id":-1,"group_type":""},{"Index":2,"Type":"paragraph","Text":"• In particular, if we have $n$ subjects and $m$ objects, then the access control matrix has $n$ rows, $m$ columns, and $n \\cdot m$ cells.","Level":0,"Polygon":{"LeftBottom":{"X":222,"Y":733},"LeftTop":{"X":222,"Y":587},"RightBottom":{"X":2564,"Y":733},"RightTop":{"X":2564,"Y":587}},"InsetImageName":"","Elements":null,"ImagePath":"","group_id":-1,"group_type":""},{"Index":3,"Type":"paragraph","Text":"● For example, a reasonably sized computer server could easily have 1,000 subjects, who are its users, and 1,000,000 objects, which are its files and directories.","Level":0,"Polygon":{"LeftBottom":{"X":222,"Y":951},"LeftTop":{"X":222,"Y":749},"RightBottom":{"X":2555,"Y":951},"RightTop":{"X":2555,"Y":749}},"InsetImageName":"","Elements":null,"ImagePath":"","group_id":-1,"group_type":""},{"Index":4,"Type":"paragraph","Text":"● But this would imply an access control matrix with 1 billion cells!","Level":0,"Polygon":{"LeftBottom":{"X":326,"Y":1031},"LeftTop":{"X":326,"Y":955},"RightBottom":{"X":2114,"Y":1031},"RightTop":{"X":2114,"Y":955}},"InsetImageName":"","Elements":null,"ImagePath":"","group_id":-1,"group_type":""},{"Index":5,"Type":"paragraph","Text":"● It is hard to imagine there is a system administrator anywhere on the planet with enough time and patience to fill in all the cells for a table this large!","Level":0,"Polygon":{"LeftBottom":{"X":222,"Y":1190},"LeftTop":{"X":222,"Y":1044},"RightBottom":{"X":2659,"Y":1190},"RightTop":{"X":2659,"Y":1044}},"InsetImageName":"","Elements":null,"ImagePath":"","group_id":-1,"group_type":""},{"Index":6,"Type":"paragraph","Text":"● Also, nobody would be able to view this table all at once!","Level":0,"Polygon":{"LeftBottom":{"X":222,"Y":1287},"LeftTop":{"X":222,"Y":1206},"RightBottom":{"X":2068,"Y":1287},"RightTop":{"X":2068,"Y":1206}},"InsetImageName":"","Elements":null,"ImagePath":"","group_id":-1,"group_type":""}]}